data.description: Showings began 10/29 on this charming 3 bed/2 bath St. Charles home offers a beautiful blend of tile and wood flooring that leads you to an open living area, flowing effortlessly into the kitchen. With plenty of counter space and custom cabinets, complete with under-counter lighting and slide-outs, culinary creations will be a breeze. Catch up with loved ones in the cozy adjoining family room, featuring a unique bay window & a chilled-out vibe. The separate dining area doubles as a home office or a massive playroom for kiddos. Unwind in the spacious master bedroom, complete with his-and-her closets and private bathroom. Nestled on a dead-end street, the fenced backyard offers lush greenery, a serene tree line, and a babbling creek. Other perks include an unfinished LL, generous garage with a backyard entrance, upgraded 200-amp e-panel & new roof 7/2023. Conveniently located, this haven is a hop, skip, and jump away from highways and shopping, making it a prime spot to lay down roots.
